data.name: lblStartMessage.Text
data.value:
Otacon : Ok snake it seems some weird creatures or extraterestials or... or.........something have escaped from a government facility. watch yourself out there Snake. Oh and try and protect those civilians too. Have you enough ammo?
Snake : Of coures, infinite ammo remember.

data.name: lblTutorial.Text
data.value: Here's a quick tutorial : press"W" to move up. press "A" to move left. press "S" to move down. press "D" to move right. press "F" to shoot. To change the difficulty either click on the button or press space. Get used to the controls before you start(press the green button).
